  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Curfew will not be taken into account, come to the protest tomorrow - United People's Power",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United People's Shakti has called on everyone to disregard the police curfew and gather near the Kurakottai railway station tomorrow.",
        "A police curfew will be enforced in Colombo North, South, Madthi, Nugegoda, Kelani and Negombo Police Divisions from 9pm tonight until further notice.",
        "In this case, the police curfew has been enforced while the people are preparing for a big protest against the government tomorrow.",
        "It is noteworthy that the United People's Shakti has called for everyone to gather near the Kurakottai railway station tomorrow, disregarding the police curfew."
      ],
